		</div>

		<div class="list-description" itemprop="description">
							
<p>With any of these five simple recipes, 30 minutes on a Sunday night can translate into a week’s worth of wholesome, hearty breakfasts.</p>					</div>

					<p class="sByline">- 
		
	
				
				
	Melina Vissat,&nbsp;<span class="ui-staffline">Contributor</span></p>
				
		

		
	
				
					
